        <style type="text/css">
            body {
                background: lightgray;
            }
            .container {
                position: absolute;
                z-index: 1;
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                background: #0F0;
            }
            .blender {
                background: #0F0;
                margin: 50px;
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                mix-blend-mode: difference;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Test passes if you can see two green squares and a black square as their intersection,<br />
            drawn over a light gray background.</p>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="blender"></div>
        </div>
    

